PN,43301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,FA woman from Plymouth with stage three
OL,7,Fcancer remains stranded in Dubai, just
OL,8,Fdays before her chemotherapy is due to
OL,9,Fget underway at Derriford Hospital.
OL,11,FLinzi Stone was meant to start
OL,12,Fchemotherapy on Friday, but she has no
OL,13,Fidea if she will make it back in time
OL,14,Fbecause flights across the Gulf have
OL,15,Fbeen cancelled for days amid the US-
OL,16,FIsraeli war with Iran.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
