OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,FThe 47-year-old had travelled to Dubai
OL,7,Fwith her husband Paul, and their 11-
OL,8,Fyear-old daughter, Summer, for a
OL,9,Fholiday before her treatment got
OL,10,Funderway.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country, Mrs
OL,13,FStone's husband said: "We decided to
OL,14,Fgo all out and have a lovely break
OL,15,Fbefore she started Chemotherapy, which
OL,16,Fwe got authorisation from the doctors
OL,17,Fto do.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,F"Her chemo is starting on Friday, so
OL,7,Fwe came here to get five days of
OL,8,Frelaxation, and it's not turned out
OL,9,Fthat way."
OL,11,FThe family had been due to fly back on
OL,12,FSunday morning, but their flight was
OL,13,Fcancelled after the US and Israel
OL,14,Flaunched strikes against Iran.
OL,16,FThey were told they would be able to
OL,17,Freturn on Monday 2 March, but their
OL,18,Freplacement flight was also cancelled.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,FMr Stone said they are now due to
OL,7,Freturn on Wednesday 4 March, but they
OL,8,Fhave no idea if the flight will
OL,9,Factually take off.
OL,11,F"From what I can gather, Virgin
OL,12,Fflights were cancelled today and I
OL,13,Fhave a feeling it won't be the case,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"It's frustrating. My wife is
OL,17,Fobviously desperate to get home and
OL,18,Fstart her chemotherapy, and panicking
OL,19,Fthat every day she misses the chemo
OL,20,Fthings are going to get worse.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,F"She's in a bit of pain, so it's not a
OL,7,Fgood place to be."
OL,9,FThe family are staying in a hotel on
OL,10,FThe Palm in Dubai near Jebel Ali Port.
OL,12,FThey were sitting by the hotel's
OL,13,Fswimming pool on Saturday afternoon
OL,14,Fwhen there was an explosion directly
OL,15,Fabove them. They later found out it
OL,16,Fwas an Iraqi drone being shot down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,F"A lot of people started running into
OL,7,Fthe hotel, not knowing what was going
OL,8,Fon, and it was only when we got inside
OL,9,Fthat someone said war had broken out.
OL,10,FIt was all a bit surreal."
OL,12,FMr Stone said they were told to stay
OL,13,Finside the hotel for two days. He said
OL,14,Fthey are now able go outside to use
OL,15,Fthe hotel's facilities, but have to
OL,16,Fstay inside the grounds.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,F"We haven't had a lot of sleep," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "There are a lot of fighter jets
OL,8,Fgoing across the skies and drones
OL,9,Fbeing shot down. That was quite
OL,10,Fintense, and when you have a young
OL,11,Ffamily, they are panicking a bit to
OL,12,Fsay the least."
OL,14,FMr Stone said he is doing everything
OL,15,Fhe can to support his wife and 11-year-
OL,16,Fold daughter.
OL,18,F"Obviously, when you have got bombs
OL,19,Fgoing off she does get frightened," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,F"For my wife, with everything she's
OL,7,Fbeen going through already, this is an
OL,8,Fissue she doesn't really need in any
OL,9,Fway, shape or form."
OL,11,FMr Stone thanked his family and
OL,12,Ffriends in Plymouth who have been
OL,13,Fregularly checking up on them.
OL,15,F"My phone has been going non-stop," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "They've all been fantastic."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1772618689
OL,3,CCancer patient stranded in Dubai days
OL,4,Cbefore chemotherapy is due to start
OL,6,F"I've got friends looking after our
OL,7,Fdogs and told them they might have to
OL,8,Fhave them a bit longer. It's times
OL,9,Flike these you realise how important
OL,10,Fyour friends are, and they have been
OL,11,Famazing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
